{"tid":792883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國惠台一場空！台商西進被唬弄「政策改了」","createTime":"2018-08-25T02:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T00:43:21.000Z","uid":35790,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"88eca904133b313c5ea787ce79f534b6d77e7584","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"中國惠台一場空！台商西進被唬弄「政策改了」<br />\n<br />\n2018-08-25 08:43<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國2月提出對台31項措施，各省市陸續推出實施辦法，企圖拉攏台灣青年赴中國。對此陸委會成立專案小組追蹤監控，日前報告出爐顯示，中國青創基地成功率不到3％。有曾經在中國青創基地創業的台灣年輕人，向媒體透露，到中國實際待了一年，只拿到房租補助，其他全跳票，被騙過去，對方才稱「政策改了」。<br />\n<br />\n《三立新聞網》報導，一名曾在中國青創基地創業的謝小姐透露，當初對方承諾一年內免房租，並補助員工薪資、協助「對接」資金，但一年下來卻只拿到房租補助，其他全都跳票，只好退場。<br />\n<br />\n謝小姐說，對方向她表示，沒有辦法給出原本的承諾，因為「政策有改變」。她也透露，中國各地祭出的「福利」不同。以自己為例，基地幹部承諾第一年「物業費」免費，也就是辦公室房租、地租，大約提供5、6人的空間；此外，補貼員工薪水、經營有成的話，還能幫忙「對接」資金和市場，但最後一場空，都是「說一套做一套」，她一年後決定退出。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2530495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2530495&d=B7GgB8pnYMoULr9Hm87hWZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7a1988e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2530495&h=76ef7253\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2530495</a>"},{"pid":"89503ba7967cfe5833bd7b08a6614674c23a9cd0","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"攞居民證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495012664fac0fceb2cf74caa5fe6a0e58ac35c9","tid":792883,"uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"89503ba7967cfe5833bd7b08a6614674c23a9cd0","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"攞居民證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"權利冇曬就話政策改左<br />\n<br />\n責任稅款就不斷加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e85ff8d889c56f212fc26a975d6cb0a9f73536","tid":792883,"uid":88862,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"535844a4604f62da91aa1cee11759ddd3af3fe71","tid":792883,"uid":44454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"相信中國人嘅都係死有餘辜"},{"pid":"bd7150d5b583d749fe3327cbf5027c1b3948679a","tid":792883,"uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"仲信支那真係戇撚鳩冇藥醫！"},{"pid":"2e98eb960b4de793a460fae46f4f77e52a8bf91a","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"495012664fac0fceb2cf74caa5fe6a0e58ac35c9","tid":792883,"uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"89503ba7967cfe5833bd7b08a6614674c23a9cd0","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"攞居民證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"權利冇曬就話政策改左<br />\n<br />\n責任稅款就不斷加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"打完手指模 影埋相入檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86976dc004ebf96deb632b59f6018c25157f8fff","tid":792883,"uid":522,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"有油水中國人自己袋左先 仲會益你外人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03db9e2efc0f1406ecbd3598c0e6825fd5d276b","tid":792883,"uid":42435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:51:18.000Z","msg":"支那都好信"},{"pid":"ba1ac7f0a02ea996deed848a4945cbaabc7e348f","tid":792883,"uid":46527,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/105235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F105235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f232ddae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58268cca51bf687c8fcf954612b2326bf9c92255","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"與台斷交後？這些前友邦4億美元金援落空、愛滋氾濫<br />\n<br />\n2018/08/22 23:43<br />\n<br />\n近日薩爾瓦多突宣布與我國斷交，轉向中國建交，台灣邦交國剩下17國，而薩國也是台灣2年來第5個斷交友邦。反觀先前與我國斷交的友邦國現金發展如何？有的失去承諾好的金援，也有的建設停擺，還有國家淪陷愛滋病風暴，民不聊生。<br />\n<br />\n與台灣斷交的友邦國，大多是接受中國大陸金援而轉向建交，而大陸的方式，大多是開出天價，承諾會給予經濟援助，並投注資金大興建設，但也傳出許多開發中地區與台灣斷交後失去金援，甚至停擺。<br />\n<br />\n哥斯大黎加在2007年宣布和台灣斷交，中國大陸曾承諾，會提供哥斯大黎加4億美元蓋高速公路，但至今已經過10年，卻是一點下文都沒有，讓哥斯大黎加當年普天同慶的大動土木開工，現在只能停擺在那兒，連橋墩都還沒蓋出來。<br />\n<br />\n另外，剛果、甘比亞和莫三比克，當年也是接受中國大陸以幫助國內建設、挹注大量資金為誘因和我國斷交，後來不但建設金沒拿到，當地人還成為大陸加工廠的血汗勞工；還有聖多美普林西比，當年要求我國投注2.1億美金的金援，卻被我國以「堅持健康外交」為由拒絕，因此斷交，但大陸承諾的1.4億美元至今沒有下文，就連機場擴建的工程也無限延期。<br />\n<br />\n而馬拉威當年也被大陸以60億美元的天價，利誘與我國斷交，雖然有得到金援拓展基礎建設，但是醫療卻陷入困境，由於大陸醫療團隊缺乏周詳計畫，使得愛滋病在馬拉威氾濫，1年多達8萬人死於愛滋病；馬拉威總統事後還對和台灣斷交一事大嘆後悔，但大陸的空頭支票，讓他們進退兩難，民不聊生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/978785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fpolitics%2F978785&d=B7GgB8pnYMoULr9Hm87hWZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3349285e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/978785</a>"},{"pid":"f908c1842321b910fd1f70306cfb155fc541c50a","tid":792883,"uid":57346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86976dc004ebf96deb632b59f6018c25157f8fff","tid":792883,"uid":522,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"有油水中國人自己袋左先 仲會益你外人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"你錯喇！有油水係共產黨人袋左先，中國人不過係奴隸，益外人都唔會益中國人，引左入坑既台灣人啫係中國人，唔劏你劏邊個！"},{"pid":"727f625c77c3d40ee404afa6d5b209b63b168dda","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明已係歷史文件<br />\n基本法最終解釋權在人大"},{"pid":"a4d4f20b179845de498fa6d28ffdbc9ab40c3a18","tid":792883,"uid":72777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:20:11.000Z","msg":"信中共? 自己擺黎賤<br />\n劏左你黎食, 剩底D骨仲要攞黎煲湯呀懵撚"},{"pid":"2ff503107a10078e56e0c1044b0273a3d2d62383","tid":792883,"uid":153689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"中國傳統不嬲都係講一套做一套<br />\n第一日先知？"},{"pid":"64053601d98108ec881c58bbad65629f4f9df939","tid":792883,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"政策任佢改<br />\n龍門隨佢搬"},{"pid":"c6e5d1426be6978eaf794204aa1ed96e9ad833d0","tid":792883,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495012664fac0fceb2cf74caa5fe6a0e58ac35c9","tid":792883,"uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"89503ba7967cfe5833bd7b08a6614674c23a9cd0","tid":792883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"攞居民證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"權利冇曬就話政策改左<br />\n<br />\n責任稅款就不斷加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5cb410b4135495ffe61c617876ad624b072628","tid":792883,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b51d6a8d78c40ce0ad7bcf6551c3370d7e55da1","tid":792883,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgm